Name: jingor sudoku
About the game: Jingor Sudoku is a puzzle game, can be used as a hobby, can challenge intelligence, can be leisure entertainment. Jingor Sudoku is to fill the number between 1 and 8 in Jingor face (the expanding surface of the cube) with some numbers in accordance with the following two rules into the blank nine grid except the middle grid. Rule 1: Each number can appear only once in the same side. The middle grid of the ninth grid is invalid. There are 6 sides. Rule 2: Each number can appear only once in the same edge. There are 12 edges. Summary rule: that is, each number from 1 to 8 can only appear once on each side or edge. It is emphasized that the answer to each Jingor Sudoku is unique The same edge refers to the 8 cells involved by the edge in the cube.
